      • rerun

        public static void rerun(boolean wb,
                         int repositoryType)

        calls the different function tests:

        medianTest(boolean, int)

        smallestTest(boolean, int)

        gradeTest(boolean, int)

        checkSumTest(boolean, int)

        syllablesTest(boolean, int)

        tip: running all of those tests at the same time will take very long; comment unnecessary ones out.

        Parameters:
        wb - wb = whitebox and determines whether the program will run a whitebox test(true) or a blackbox one(false).
        repositoryType - which repository the program should use to repair the faulty functions. repository type: 0 linux, 1 introclass, 2 future
